<item>
            <title>[LU-12425] Add test for splice_read</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12425</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Lustre supports splice read, but does not have any tests for it - The word &apos;splice&apos; doesn&apos;t appear in the /tests subdirectory at all.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We should add at least one test for this, and we should also add something to the new sanity 127c for extents_stats.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are some GPL licensed LTP tests that we could copy from:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/linux-test-project/ltp/tree/master/testcases/kernel/syscalls/splice&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/linux-test-project/ltp/tree/master/testcases/kernel/syscalls/splice&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
